Instructions for Ball World.

After launching the application, type into the textbox the type of ball that you would like to 
add to the screen. The following balls you may add are: balls.ColorChangingBall, balls.SizeChangingBall, 
and balls.StraightBall. After typing in the type of ball into the textbox, click "Add Ball" as many times
as you wish to add balls to the window. Press the "Clear Ball" to remove all balls from the screen.